      "witnesses": [
        {
          "language": "de",
          "role": "canonical_source",
          "text": "Segne den Becher, welcher \u00fcberfliessen will, dass das Wasser golden aus ihm fliesse und \u00fcberallhin den Abglanz deiner Wonne trage!"
        },
        {
          "language": "ru",
          "role": "working_translation",
          "text": "\u0411\u043b\u0430\u0433\u043e\u0441\u043b\u043e\u0432\u0438 \u0447\u0430\u0448\u0443,\n\u043a\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0440\u0430\u044f \u0445\u043e\u0447\u0435\u0442 \u043f\u0435\u0440\u0435\u043b\u0438\u0442\u044c\u0441\u044f,\n\u0447\u0442\u043e\u0431\u044b \u0437\u043e\u043b\u043e\u0442\u043e \u0438\u0437 \u043d\u0435\u0451 \u0442\u0435\u043a\u043b\u043e\n\u0438 \u043f\u043e\u0432\u0441\u044e\u0434\u0443 \u043d\u0435\u0441\u043b\u043e \u043e\u0442\u0431\u043b\u0435\u0441\u043a \u0442\u0432\u043e\u0435\u0433\u043e \u043b\u0438\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f!"
        },
        {
          "language": "en",
          "role": "bridge_translation",
          "text": "Bless the cup that wants to overflow, so that the water may flow golden from it and carry everywhere the reflection of your bliss!"
        }
      ],
      "translation_tension": {
        "segment_id": "zv1-10-overflowing-cup",
        "note": "'Abglanz' remains afterglow, reflection, or reflected radiance; witness layers should keep the difference between source light and carried shine. 'Wonne' and '\u043b\u0438\u043a\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435' keep the image affectively high without collapsing into mere pleasure."
      }
    }
